      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>juice </strong>of 1/4<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1/2] </span><strong>lemon</strong> with the <strong>mayonnaise </strong>in a small bowl</p>\n<p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>lemony mayo</strong></p>",
